          "title": "Small Group: Exclusive Rugged Hummer Adventure",
          "shortDescription": null,
          "description": "With a knowledgeable tour guide, begin touring Ketchikan in rugged luxury in a Hummer H2. Your destination options include totem pole parks, walks through the rainforest, a beach walk, a stop at Herring Cove to look for wildlife in season, waterfall viewing, Ward Lake in the Tongass National Forest, and more. Whatever you choose to do, the state of the art H2 will take you on the adventure of a lifetime in both style and comfort. Note: tour price is per vehicle.",
